OL,3,C'Spiral of doom': Girl, 8, loses hair
OL,4,Camid Israel's bombardment of Gaza
OL,6,FA group of leading UK charities are
OL,7,Ftonight launching a joint appeal for
OL,8,Furgently needed humanitarian aid for
OL,9,Fmillions of people in Gaza, Lebanon
OL,10,Fand across the Middle East. Caught in
OL,11,Fthe middle are the youngest and most
OL,12,Fvulnerable victims, as ITV News
OL,13,FCorrespondent John Ray reports
OL,15,FWar consumes so much and leaves its
OL,16,Fvictims with so little. For an eight-
OL,17,Fyear-old girl in Gaza, called Sama,
OL,18,Fit's her dignity that's been lost.
