OL,3,C'Spiral of doom': Girl, 8, loses hair
OL,4,Camid Israel's bombardment of Gaza
OL,6,FIt takes her some courage to remove
OL,7,Fher pink head scarf. Her once
OL,8,Fbeautiful hair is gone. It is a
OL,9,Fmeasure of her trauma.
OL,11,FSo too are her tears.
OL,13,F"I wish I could go back to school. To
OL,14,Fplay with my friends," she told ITV
OL,15,FNews.
OL,17,FShe's one of many thousands of Gazan
OL,18,Fchildren who have spent a year on the
OL,19,Frun from Israeli missiles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
