OL,3,C'Spiral of doom': Girl, 8, loses hair
OL,4,Camid Israel's bombardment of Gaza
OL,6,FShe now lives in a tent in the
OL,7,Fsouthern city of Khan Younis; one of
OL,8,Fmany camps for displaced people.
OL,10,FWho knows when she'll need to move
OL,11,Fagain? Who knows if she'll ever be
OL,12,Fable to return to her home in Rafa?
OL,13,F"The treatment she needs is to feel
OL,14,Fsafe," her mother said.
OL,16,F"She can't keep hearing the bombing
OL,17,Fand the sounds of ambulances. My
OL,18,Fdaughter needs her childhood back."
OL,20,FAccording to the Disasters Emergency
OL,21,FCommittee:
