OL,3,C'Spiral of doom': Girl, 8, loses hair
OL,4,Camid Israel's bombardment of Gaza
OL,6,FIn Lebanon, already in economic crisis
OL,7,Fbefore the war, aid agencies have
OL,8,Fwarned of what they call a "spiral of
OL,9,Fdoom".
OL,11,FYou can see the humanitarian calamity
OL,12,Funfolding before your eyes in the
OL,13,Fmakeshift shelters along the seafront
OL,14,Fin Beirut.
OL,16,FAlma fled her home in the city's
OL,17,Fsuburbs two weeks ago, to try to put a
OL,18,Fsafe distance from the bombs and her
OL,19,Fgrandchildren. But it's not far enough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
