OL,3,C'Spiral of doom': Girl, 8, loses hair
OL,4,Camid Israel's bombardment of Gaza
OL,6,F"We are always afraid," she told me.
OL,7,F"When the kids hear the bombs, they
OL,8,Fsay; 'Grandma....they're hitting,
OL,9,Fthey're hitting.'"
OL,11,FWinter will arrive before too long and
OL,12,Fthere will be many families camping
OL,13,Fout on the pavement. There is a severe
OL,14,Fshortage of accommodation.
OL,16,FMore than a million people have fled
OL,17,Ftheir homes - 400,000 of them
OL,18,Fchildren. There is a desperate
OL,19,Fshortage of shelter and often other
OL,20,Flife essentials.
