OL,6,FHamas, whose fighters slaughtered so
OL,7,Fmany Israelis on October 7 ` is not
OL,8,Fyet defeated and Hezbollah's missiles
OL,9,Fstill fly across the southern border.
OL,11,FNo one on any side of these conflicts
OL,12,Fis predicting a ceasefire any time
OL,13,Fsoon. And all the while, war inflicts
